responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C785104642AF647058FA7DA5AE33122E", "So they are. I\'ve reported that their numbers are growing lately. They\'ve got a stronghold in the hills nearby, but they don\'t seem content to stay there. They make their way here to fatten their numbers with our countrymen, and their larders with our supplies. What I need is an idea where they\'re stashing their take. They can\'t be dragging it all back to the hills one sack at a time...")
